@startuml system-context
!theme plain
title System Context Diagram -- [Project Name]

' Instructions: Replace placeholders with your system details

actor "User Role 1" as user1
actor "User Role 2" as user2

rectangle "System Name" as system {
}

rectangle "External System 1" as ext1
database "External DB" as extdb

user1 --> system : HTTPS
user2 --> system : HTTPS
system --> ext1 : REST API
system --> extdb : Protocol

note right of system
  Replace with your system boundary
  and all external actors/systems
end note
@enduml
